doctype html
html(lang='en')
  head
    meta(charset='UTF-8')
    meta(http-equiv='X-UA-Compatible' content='IE=edge')
    meta(name='viewport' content='width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0')
    link(rel='preconnect' href='https://fonts.googleapis.com')
    link(rel='preconnect' href='https://fonts.gstatic.com' crossorigin='')
    link(href='https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@400;500&display=swap' rel='stylesheet')
    script(src='https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/Chart.js/2.9.4/Chart.js')
    title shoorah PDF
  body
    div(style='width: 800px;height: 1024px;margin: auto;')
      // A4 size
      div(style='border: 2px solid #4A56DB;')
      div(style='padding: 30px 30px 0px 30px;')
        div(style='display: flex;flex-direction: row;justify-content: space-between;align-items: center;')
          div
            h1(style="font-family: 'Poppins';width: auto;height: 21px;font-style: normal;font-weight: 400;font-size: 16px;line-height: 21px;color: #18202F;margin: 0;")
              | Breathwork Report 
          div
            img(src='https://d12231i07r54en.cloudfront.net/app_configs/pdf_shoorah_logo.png' alt='shoorah-logo' style='width: 120px;height: 20px;')
        div(style='display: flex;flex-direction: row;justify-content: center;align-items: center;width: 100%;height: 41px;background: #4A56DB;border-radius: 10px;margin: 40px 0px 30px 0px;')
          p(style="width: auto;height: 21px;font-family: 'Poppins';font-style: normal;font-weight: 500;font-size: 14px;line-height: 21px;color: #FFFFFF;margin: 0;")
            | Report at #{locals.fromDate}
        div(style='position:relative;margin: 50px 0px 0px 0px;width: 95%;height: 250px;border: 1px dashed rgba(24, 32, 47, 0.4);\
        border-radius: 10px;padding: 16px;display: flex;flex-direction: row;justify-content: space-between;align-items: center;')
          div(style='display: flex;flex-direction: column;justify-content: space-between;width: 100%;height: auto;')
            h1(style="width: auto;height: auto;font-family: 'Poppins';font-style: normal;font-weight: 700;font-size: 20px;line-height: 30px;text-align: left;color: #18202F;margin: 0;")
              | What is Breathwork Session ? 
            p(style="width: 100%;height: 54px;font-family:Poppins;font-style: normal;font-weight: 400;font-size: 16px;line-height: 18px;text-align: left;                    \
            color: #18202F;margin: 10px 0px 0px 0px;")
              | #{locals.breathworkMessage} Breathwork sessions typically involve guided breathing exercises aimed at facilitating various physical, emotional, and mental benefits. These sessions are often led by trained facilitators or practitioners who guide participants through specific breathing techniques and patterns.
            p(style="width: 100%;height: 54px;font-family: 'Poppins';font-style: normal;font-weight: 400;font-size: 12px;line-height: 18px;text-align: left;                    \
            color: #18202F;margin: 40px 0px 10px 0px;")
              | #{locals.breathworkMessage2} Breathwork sessions may take place in a variety of settings, including yoga studios, wellness centers, retreats, or online platforms. They can be conducted one-on-one or in group settings, and may range in duration from a few minutes to several hours.
          
      
        div(style='display: flex;width:100%;flex-direction:row;gap:20px;justify-content:center;margin: 40px 0px 0px 0px;')
            div(style='height:300px;width:50%;border-radius:10px;padding-left:20px;padding-right:20px;background-color:#6167E8;display:flex;flex-direction:column;')
             p(style='font-family:Poppins;margin-bottom:20px;width:100%;color:#fff;font-size:28px')
               | Total Breathwork Sessions Taken
             p(style='width:100%;margin-bottom:20px;color:#fff;font-size:38px;font-weight:bold')
               | #{locals.reportData.sessions} times
             
            div(style='height:300px;width:50%;border-radius:10px;padding-left:20px;padding-right:20px;display:flex;flex-direction:column;background-color:#313B6B;')
             p(style='height:auto;font-family:Poppins;margin-bottom:20px;width:100%;color:#fff;font-size:28px')
               | Total Durations Sessions Used
             p(style='height:auto;width:100%;margin-bottom:20px;;color:#fff;font-size:38px;font-weight:bold')
               | #{locals.reportData.duration} mins
             
        
        div(style='margin-top: 30px;width: 100%;height: auto;')
          p(style="margin: 0;font-family: 'Poppins';font-style: normal;font-weight: 400;font-size: 11px;line-height: 14px;color: #727272;")
        p(style="margin: 280px 0px 10px 0px;text-align: center;width: auto;height: auto;font-family: Poppins;font-style: normal;font-weight: 300;font-size: 13px;line-height: 15px;color: #727272;")
          | This Breathwork report is generated from the Shoorah Ltd mobile app ❤️
    script.
